Modify `src/acp-agent.ts` to initialize and manage the sandbox.

## Changes to ClaudeAcpAgent class

### New private fields
```typescript
private sandboxConfig?: SandboxConfig;
private sandboxInitialized: boolean = false;
```

### New imports
```typescript
import { SandboxManager, SandboxViolationStore } from '@anthropic-ai/sandbox-runtime';
import { SandboxConfig, toSandboxRuntimeConfig } from './sandbox.js';
```

### Modify `initialize()` method
- Extract `params._meta?.sandbox` as `SandboxConfig`
- If `enabled`, call `initializeSandbox(config)`

### New `initializeSandbox()` method
```typescript
private async initializeSandbox(config: SandboxConfig): Promise<void> {
  const runtimeConfig = toSandboxRuntimeConfig(config);
  await SandboxManager.initialize(runtimeConfig);
  this.sandboxConfig = config;
  this.sandboxInitialized = true;

  SandboxViolationStore.onViolation((violation) => {
    this.logger.log('Sandbox violation:', violation);
  });
}
```

### New `isSandboxed()` method
```typescript
isSandboxed(): boolean {
  return this.sandboxInitialized;
}
```

### Cleanup on shutdown
- Call `SandboxManager.reset()` when agent terminates

